reviewText: Simple and amazing exercises to help you feel better in your body and in your mind! Beautyful and helpful!

You absolutely must experience the phenomenon of Zuleikha. Unique and brilliant as a performer, here she uses another of her strong talents, which is helping people to "get into their bodies" and out of their heads for a moment.
Zuleikha has a natural gift(plus a lietime of work) of being able to pull you into her magical world of the dance. Dance Sister Dance!
